flowchart TD
    A[Load songs.csv] --> B[Read one song row]
    B --> C[Start score at 0]
    C --> D{Genre matches favorite_genre?}
    D -- Yes --> E[Add 2.0 points]
    D -- No --> F[Add 0 points]
    E --> G{Mood matches favorite_mood?}
    F --> G
    G -- Yes --> H[Add 1.0 point]
    G -- No --> I[Add 0 points]
    H --> J[Compare energy, tempo_bpm, valence, danceability, acousticness to user profile]
    I --> J
    J --> K[Add similarity points based on closeness]
    K --> L[Save final score for this song]
    L --> M{More songs left?}
    M -- Yes --> B
    M -- No --> N[Sort all songs by score]
    N --> O[Return ranked list / top 3 recommendations]
